><span style="font-size:\r\n     9.0pt;font-family:" arial","sans-serif";mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman""=""><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: black; text-align: left; line-height: 12.75pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;\r\n     font-family:" arial","sans-serif";mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman""="">Trẻ\r\n     em từ 5 – 8 tuổi giá 50% giá tour người lớn, bố mẹ đi kèm và tự chăm sóc.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:" arial","sans-serif";mso-fareast-font-family:="" "times="" new="" roman""=""><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: black; text-align: left; line-height: 12.75pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;\r\n     font-family:" arial","sans-serif";mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman""="">Trẻ\r\n     em từ 9 – 11 tuổi giá 75% giá tour người lớn.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:" arial","sans-serif";mso-fareast-font-family:="" "times="" new="" roman""=""><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: black; text-align: left; line-height: 12.75pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;\r\n     font-family:" arial","sans-serif";mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman""="">12\r\n     tuổi trở lên giá người lớn.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\r\n     " arial","sans-serif";mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman""=""><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="color: black; text-align: left; line-height: 12.75pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;\r\n     font-family:" arial","sans-serif";mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman""="">Du\r\n     khách mang theo chứng minh thư nhân dân hoặc hộ chiếu.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:" arial","sans-serif";mso-fareast-font-family:="" "times="" new="" roman""=""><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>', '<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:0in;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\njustify"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Chương trình<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><em><span style="font-family:" arial","sans-serif""=""><a href="http://halongsensetravel.com/tour-du-lich-ha-long-c.html" title="Du lich ha long sense"><strong><span style="color: black;">du lịch&nbsp;Hạ Long</span></strong></a></span></em><span class="apple-converted-space"><b><i>&nbsp;</i></b></span><strong><i><span style="font-family:" arial","sans-serif""="">– Đảo Tuần Châu</span></i></strong><span class="apple-converted-space"><i>&nbsp;</i></span>2 ngày 1 đêm đưa quý khách khám\r\nphá di sản thiên nhiên thế giời<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><a href="http://vietsensetravel.com/du-lich-ha-long-c.html"><em><b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(23, 66, 121); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">vịnh Hạ Long v</span></b